{"lastModified":1748874452099,"uri":"c::7819307041::vessel::8071c810-3afe-11f0-897b-c55069cffb02","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nWhether you’re planning a romantic getaway, an unforgettable family holiday or a solo adventure, we have the boat to suit you. This 42ft catamaran yacht offers the ideal environment for relaxation and discovery. With a 70m² mainsail area, spacious cabins, light-filled saloon and outdoor areas perfect for contemplation, every moment spent on board is simply an invitation to serenity and well-being.\n\nThe spacious saloon is laid out in the spirit and DNA of Fountaine Pajot and the U-shaped galley stands out for its user-friendliness. These spaces are connected to the helm station, plenty large enough to seat two, safely offering a perfect view of the sail plan, making it ideal for handling.\n\nOrganise dinners under the stars, set off to discover exotic destinations or simply let yourself be carried away by the tranquil rhythm of life at sea. On board, the world becomes your playground and every day is a new adventure to savour. The Astréa 42 embodies excellence in yachting.","blueprint":{"name":"SHANGRI-LA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::8071c810-3afe-11f0-897b-c55069cffb02::assets::54ed9320-3b00-11f0-a8a5-f76d376bed4c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::8071c810-3afe-11f0-897b-c55069cffb02::assets::54ecf6e1-3b00-11f0-a8a5-f76d376bed4c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::8071c810-3afe-11f0-897b-c55069cffb02::assets::54efb600-3b00-11f0-a8a5-f76d376bed4c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::8071c810-3afe-11f0-897b-c55069cffb02::assets::54ee5670-3b00-11f0-a8a5-f76d376bed4c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::8071c810-3afe-11f0-897b-c55069cffb02::assets::54eb2220-3b00-11f0-a8a5-f76d376bed4c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::8071c810-3afe-11f0-897b-c55069cffb02::assets::54f66cc0-3b00-11f0-a8a5-f76d376bed4c/{imageVariant}",